{"tid":2235033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"西九龍中心外牆現漫畫少女泳裝廣告　民建聯區議員投訴意識不良促拆除","createTime":"2020-10-08T10:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T14:44:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d33d7828c149bb9f37934a131f51b3e950774430","tid":2235033,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"深水埗西九龍中心外牆近月掛上由本地漫畫家林祥焜創作大型漫畫廣告，廣告中少女穿上泳裝，配上「不忘初心」等字眼。民建聯深水埗區議員劉佩玉稱接獲大量家長投訴，指少女「衣著暴露」， 「影射出不良意識」，有家長稱子女看到該廣告後感到不安，擔心廣告發放出來的訊息會為學生帶來不良影響，今早（10 月 8 日）聯同深水埗社區幹事陳穎欣等前往西九龍中心請願，要求拆除該廣告。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒人車淑梅昨日在 facebook 發文，也稱被廣告「嚇一跳」。創作廣告的林祥焜在 facebook 隔空回應，「點解妳（車淑梅）今時今日變得咁守舊？我真係好傷心！」他在另一帖文又嘲諷道：「我幾驚冇人幫手宣傳！多謝都嚟唔切！下一步封沙灘泳池，捉晒啲三點式女泳客佢，好嘢」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%96%E7%89%86%E7%8F%BE%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%9D%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E6%84%8F%E8%AD%98%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E4%BF%83%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4/?fbclid=IwAR3PIb2oJxDX2NqDWYVAUunfIm2Vb1bsxBD_Aod6V2inVm4zQJitX6xV9WI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%2589%2586%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E8%25A3%259D%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25AD%2598%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2589%25AF%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%258B%2586%25E9%2599%25A4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3PIb2oJxDX2NqDWYVAUunfIm2Vb1bsxBD_Aod6V2inVm4zQJitX6xV9WI&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=7f27c497\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2